This looks like a bug in msys2 shipped `mingw-w64-x86_64-gcc-libs 7.2.0-1`, might be caused by this: https://github.com/mirror/mingw-w64/commit/2e64b9e4537d564478f17b873b2f655f518325ed. Or it could be some bad interaction of this with Rust, not sure if Rust is using it's own shipped tools here.
